item.description: A consulting project for a solar energy based start-up to understand potential customers based on customer sign-ups. The goal of this project was help the management understand features influencing customer sign-ups - Recommended marketing channels and optimization of mobile website. Also advised a third party vendor for easier access of data for future use.
